Package com.rays.bean

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DropdownListBean
    The DropdownListBean interface defines methods required for populating dropdown lists in UI components.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseBean
    The BaseBean class serves as a base class for other beans, providing common properties like id, createdBy, modifiedBy, createdDatetime, and modifiedDatetime.
    CollegeBean
    The CollegeBean class represents a college entity and contains details such as name, address, state, city, and phone number.
    CourseBean
    The CourseBean class represents a course entity, containing details such as course name, duration, and description.
    FacultyBean
    The FacultyBean class represents a faculty member entity, containing personal and academic details such as name, contact information, date of birth, associated college, course, and subject.
    MarksheetBean
    The MarksheetBean class represents the academic marksheet of a student.
    RoleBean
    The RoleBean class represents a user role in the system, such as Admin, Faculty, Student, Kiosk, or College.
    StudentBean
    The StudentBean class represents a student entity with personal and academic details such as name, date of birth, gender, contact information, and college association.
    SubjectBean
    The SubjectBean class represents a subject entity that is associated with a specific course.
    TimeTableBean
    The TimeTableBean class represents a timetable entry for exams, including information about the semester, exam date and time, course, subject, and description.
    UserBean
    The UserBean class represents a system user with personal details, login credentials, and role-based access information.
